{
  "text": "The migration capacity of CFBs was evaluated by scratch assay as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Briefly, The CFBs were plated on 6-well plates and grown to about 90% confluence. An artificial gap was generated by scratching with a sterile pipette tip. The width of the gap was measured at 24 h intervals.",
  "correct_citation": {
